u003eFix\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe issue was mitigated.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"reasoning\"\u003eReasoning\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAn XSS as such is not a huge issue from a risk perspective, although it poses a small risk for stealing of credentials. Open redirects allow for far more sophisticated attack vectors using mass phishing emails and a customized malicious login page.\u003c/p\u003e\n"},{"category":"researcher","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false}]}